  22:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * è‹¥ن¸چéœ€è¦پهٹ¨و€پè°ƒو•´é‡ڈوµ‹هگ‘é‡ڈzï¼Œهڈ¯ç®€هچ•ه°†ç»“و‍„ن½“ن¸­çڑ„Use_Auto_Adjustmentهˆ‌ه§‹هŒ–ن
  23:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * ه§‹هŒ–çں©éکµPé‚£و ·ç”¨ه¸¸è§„و–¹ه¼ڈهˆ‌ه§‹هŒ–z H Rهچ³هڈ¯م€‚
  24:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * If automatic adjustment is not required, assign zero to the UseAutoAdjustment
  25:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * and initialize z H R in the normal way as matrix P.
  26:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  *
